\begin{equation}
    \theta_1 = \theta_2= 54.7356103172^{\circ} \text{ (balance point for photon sphere and ISCO)}
\end{equation}
or approximately $\theta_1 = \theta_2 \approx 0.9553\,\text{radians}$.

